   "source": [
    "# Token Testing Notebook\n",
    "\n",
    "This notebook tests Groq API token calculations separately from the main Code-M8 codebase.\n",
    "\n",
    "## Goals\n",
    "1. Verify actual API token usage vs estimates\n",
    "2. Test different token estimation methods\n",
    "3. Compare tiktoken vs character division"
   ]
  },
